# MARBLE SACRED — ONLYFANSSEARCH RULES

## These rules have been broken 20+ times. Each time cost hours of work and Cursor credits. NEVER AGAIN.

## BEFORE YOU TOUCH ANY ONLYFANSSEARCH FILE

STOP. Read this checklist:

- [ ] Did the owner EXPLICITLY ask for this change?
- [ ] Does this change violate ANY rule below?
- [ ] Will this change cause a link to go to OnlyFans instead of Erogram?
- [ ] Will this change navigate away from the search page instead of opening a new tab?
- [ ] Will this change show hidden categories on the main page?

If ANY answer is wrong → **DO NOT MAKE THE CHANGE. Ask the owner first.**

---

## RULE 1: ALL creator links open in a NEW TAB

Every single creator link on `/onlyfanssearch` MUST open in a new tab/window. NO EXCEPTIONS.

- Use `window.open(url, '_blank', 'noopener,noreferrer')` for JS click handlers
- Use `target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"` for `<a>` tags
- Registration/login redirects ALSO open in new tab — NEVER use `window.location.href`
- This applies to: CreatorCard, Top10CategoryCard, Trending on Erogram, Featured creators, Recently Added
- NEVER navigate away from the search page. The user must stay on `/onlyfanssearch`.

## RULE 2: Creator links use `/{username}-onlyfans` — NEVER `/onlyfans/{username}`

All creator profile links point to `/{username}-onlyfans` (the public Erogram creator page).

- NEVER link to `/onlyfans/{username}` — that route redirects non-logged-in users to OnlyFans
- NEVER link directly to OnlyFans URLs (creator.url) from the search page
- Non-logged-in users go to `/join-erogram?redirect=/{username}-onlyfans` (in new tab)
- Logged-in users go to `/{username}-onlyfans` (in new tab)
- The ONLY place a user leaves Erogram is from the creator's own profile page CTA button

## RULE 3: These 16 categories are HIDDEN on the main page pills

HIDDEN (never show on `/onlyfanssearch` category pills):
Ahegao, Alt, Cosplay, Streamer, Fitness, JOI, Lesbian, Tattoo, Curvy, Ebony, Feet, Lingerie, Thick, Twerk, Squirt, Piercing

SHOWN (only these 12):
Asian, Blonde, Teen, MILF, Amateur, Redhead, Goth, Petite, Big Ass, Big Boobs, Brunette, Latina

Implementation: `OF_CATEGORIES.slice(0, 12)` in the category pills section of OnlyFansClient.tsx.
The hidden categories still exist in constants.ts and still have their own pages — they are ONLY hidden from the main page pills.

- NEVER add them back to the main page
- NEVER change the slice
- NEVER reorder OF_CATEGORIES in constants.ts

## RULE 4: Trending section shows rank + name + username — NO points

The "Trending on Erogram" section shows:
- Rank number badge
- Avatar
- Creator name
- @username

It does NOT show points, pts, pointsDelta, or any numeric score. NEVER add points back.

## RULE 5: DO NOT touch these files without explicit owner permission

- `app/onlyfanssearch/constants.ts` — category/country lists, URL helpers
- `app/onlyfanssearch/ofMeta.ts` — SEO metadata for all locale variants
- `app/onlyfanssearch/sitemap.ts` — sitemap generation
- `app/onlyfanssearch/creatorBios.ts` — hand-written creator bios

## RULE 6: NEVER create API routes for onlyfanssearch features

All data fetching uses server actions in `lib/actions/`. See the no-unnecessary-api rule.

## IF YOU THINK ANY RULE SHOULD CHANGE

**STOP. Ask the owner with this exact format:**
"I want to change [RULE NUMBER] because [REASON]. Current behavior: [X]. Proposed: [Y]. Do you approve?"

**Default answer is ALWAYS: NO. Leave it alone.**
